# NovaLang Lesson Format 2.0

Format name: NovaLang Lesson Format 2.0
Status: Frozen
Reference implementation: ja-daily_life-m01-u1-l1
Last approved by project owner: 2026-07-13

> **Superseded for Q14 only (2026-07-15):** the project owner approved a
> breaking change to Q14's behavior. See
> `.cursor/rules/04_novalang_lesson_format_3_0.mdc` for the current Q14
> contract (non-graded Real-World Practice dialogue,
> `real_world_practice_dialogue`). This file is kept unmodified elsewhere as
> the historical record of what was approved on 2026-07-13; its Q14 row and
